Sophie Winkleman https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sophie_Winkleman 0 Sophie Winkleman (born 5 August 1980) is an English actress. She is the wife of Lord Frederick Windsor, son of Queen Elizabeth II's first cousin Prince Michael of Kent, and as such is also known as Lady Frederick Windsor.
